 
<p>
Driverless taxis operated by Cruise are not autonomous &mdash; they work on
remote control.  
<a href="https://www.wired.com/story/cruises-robot-car-outages/">If they lose communication with the base, they stop.</a>
<p>
I wouldn't trust any driverless taxi if it communicates with any
server whatsoever &mdash; or if I can't use it anonymously.

 